snippet.textDisplay:
Heal Spirit basically is the replacement of Heal

The reason of Heal reworked into Heal Spirit because Heal was the lowest usage of Clash Royale cards, and the card usually place in top 10 worst cards of Clash Royale at Clash Royale guide site, the spell card's effect was reliability not work to facing many aggressive players. So developers reworked the card into Heal Spirit, bring many new useful strategies coordinate with the card, and excepting the card usage greatly increasing, become the popular card of the players in the season.

Also, the card will be OP when initially implemented, after the season the card will be nerfed at the next season begins.
